# 🚀 K3s Kubernetes Cluster on Alpine Linux (VirtualBox Home Lab)

This project documents a lightweight Kubernetes home lab built using:

- 🐧 Alpine Linux
- ☸️ K3s (Lightweight Kubernetes)
- 🖥 VirtualBox
- 🏠 Local Home Lab Environment

The goal is to create a minimal, resource-efficient Kubernetes cluster for DevOps practice, experimentation, and learning.

---

# 📌 Architecture Overview

- 1x K3s Server (Control Plane)
- 1+ K3s Agent Nodes (Workers)
- Host-only or Bridged VirtualBox Networking
- Optional: Traefik Ingress (default in K3s)

---

