# 💻 VM Requirements

| Node Type | CPU | RAM | Disk |
|-----------|-----|-----|------|
| Server    | 2   | 2GB | 20GB |
| Agent     | 2   | 2GB | 20GB |

Minimum recommended total host RAM: **8GB**

---

# 🌐 Networking Setup (VirtualBox)

Recommended: **Host-Only Adapter + NAT**

Example configuration:

- Adapter 1: NAT (Internet Access)
- Adapter 2: Host-Only (Cluster Communication)

Example IP scheme:

| Node        | IP Address     |
|------------|---------------|
| k3s-server | 192.168.56.10 |
| k3s-agent1 | 192.168.56.11 |

---

# 🐧 Alpine Linux Installation

Install minimal Alpine Linux ISO on each VM.

